Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:50.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在那崩坏的黑暗中 你哭泣的身影如此清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:59.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}冰冷的门  至今依旧紧闭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:03.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那些过往 那些梦境 那些希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这才是天空的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:20.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}随心所欲 肆意变天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:29.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}翻越吧  越向障壁的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:39.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}穿过吧  穿越世界的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如四散的尘埃般 消失无踪  白日梦

Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:50.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}壊れた暗闇　泣いてる君の影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:59.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}冷たい扉が　今でも閉ざされ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:03.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう戻れはしないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}あの日々　あの夢　あの希望は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この空は本物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:20.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}気まぐれ　突然　色を変えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:29.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}越えて　その壁の向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:39.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}潜って　行く世界の欠片が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}はがれ落ちて消えて行くわ　Daydream

Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个垃圾说是想做画画相关的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimHei\fad(1900,0)\pos(650,340)\c&H202323&\3c&H9CADAB&\bord5\be2\blur2\fs60\b1}梦{\fs40}不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷奥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你觉得祭品不合适的话 就换别人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再牺牲一个人准备就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你觉得橘勇鱼是特别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就已经把感情抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对镇上家伙们的复仇时刻马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我都明白的 雷奥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会成为你的「容器」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(准备中)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连身边最亲近的人 被梦魔盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然都没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她 我不想让她卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这与现实和幻界无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望她能画自己喜欢的画就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我把你吵醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在画什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样 是没有什么梦想的画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明考试就近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 梦路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜里有点儿吵对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起床看看情况 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候男人需要这样的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爸爸这么说 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏玩得有点儿不顺手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 害我白操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也多少准备准备考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有资格说别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 长翅膀的鲸鱼姑娘和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇鱼 奶茶好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦路也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你在画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种生物真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连没见过的东西都能画出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在用心眼看着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也想让在这里的眼睛看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才画出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能在这个世界相见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就说了一句「诶」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是这么有感觉的台词呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最爱的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然夫妇两人都遇难了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有那么小的孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界还真是残酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还有不少债务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没流浪街头就已经很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管心里有多么结实的城堡 它都会轻易地垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的心情 语言还有事物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中重视的东西越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西也会变得越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母 老师 同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是「仅仅在那里」一样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没有希望也没有失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说梦想还有希望什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对如同空壳一样的我 只是些碍事的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你会进入我的牢狱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许也只是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对为了向米斯特路汀复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在「现界」中寻找容器的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有感情的你是最合适不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦魔 雷斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这无间的牢狱中 成为我的容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容器…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好名字呢 容器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空空的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫河浪千鹤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草泥马哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个来店里吃东西的顾客给了我两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个我在用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个我想送给河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 小鱼大人被梦魔给…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 请将你的力量借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管会发生什么事 我都想要救勇鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 橘的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 还没有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格 行动 都还是原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是会夺取人心的坏梦魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就因为这样才危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候就会成为海格力斯的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者被米斯特路汀袭击也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没让食梦者和你一起来也是这个原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 只有打开协会的门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那个梦魔拽出来 验明真身才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还不知道是敌人还是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上 在去学校之前把勇鱼带来可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在既然不知道对方的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越早接触越好不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 今天医院和社团都没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很闲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不想打扰她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 硬来麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎么办 关于小鱼大人的梦魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被玛莉送回老家的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被绑作人质的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鱼大人的梦想也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由衣 如果你重要的人的梦想就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定 会和他是一样的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…漫长的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 找勇鱼的话在房间里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原梦路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来是找梦路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看见他 好像是出门到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等他可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常欢迎 黑咖啡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 雾岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 勇鱼和藤原还真是薄情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说过要一起来考试复习的 却拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天邀请他们 人家或许也有很多事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是有要做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「睡午觉 抱着电视直到天亮」by秋柳贵照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不算有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你刚才写的那个川柳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了逗我笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说是认真写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑你了真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是认真写的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是为了逗你笑才写的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雾岛你能笑出来 我很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就身体不好 不停地辗转在医院间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的环境中长大 渐渐的变得不再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天 我或许是受了电视的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开着玩笑读起了川柳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那是一个十分幼稚的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妹妹的脸就像太阳一样绽放出了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我 也能给别人带来欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会尽我所能 为更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来欢乐的火种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是有点儿伤感的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她很快就会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个火种一定也将我心中的火点燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句 我妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都能在汉堡店里打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经痊愈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转了这么多圈儿了都没遇见主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经掌握到了这么绝棒的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快速告诉给主人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再晚点儿说不定就会忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来把那边儿的也被卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个「容器」还有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来跟那些家伙一样也是好伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是酸透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到幻界 我的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边白日做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边做着重复的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是欲壑难填的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是你的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要做梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能掠夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从人类的世界掠夺到幻界来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海格力斯主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兰保夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一条情报想要上报给您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说三叶的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和安琪·三叶在一起的叫做「食梦者」的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们居然想要反抗主人您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们积极对抗敌人真是勇敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她们都是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们一听说我们用人类的梦想作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对我下不了手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您快去打倒她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加同伴的数量才是要紧事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先不管她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们成不了什么气候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过不了多久 她们就会成为授戒的贡品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授戒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说那位米斯特路汀也会来这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 给我来杯热点的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前 你有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天跟你在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你说「我们一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放松了警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到你还留在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想跟我说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪 连你也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇鱼她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狡猾的树海困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 不去打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幅佳作啊 只用一天就完成了真不敢想象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不知道为什么特别顺手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是有点累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉 我们一起洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可不要偷窥哦 梦路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我说的跟变态一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是树海还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会让他对勇鱼出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇鱼她 被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候会到来的树海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候会打开的Daydream（白日梦）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在不经意间 门被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到面前的树海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到面前的梦魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫 米斯特路汀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 食梦者玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止 不会让你再对勇鱼出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimHei\fad(600,0)\pos(424,320)\bord1\blur3\3c&H656565&\b1}梦的守护者

Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:30.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天万里无云 洋溢着笑容出行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无顾忌的大吃着 香甜的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:51.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了精神 就悄悄的想起了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起裹在棉被中数着羊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在辗转难眠的夜晚 期盼天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:03.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起幻想着明天必到的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:20.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都化为坚强的心 将我笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:30.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容传递着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定会到来

Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:30.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日は青空　笑顔でお出かけ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘いお菓子　たくさん食べて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:51.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元気になると　そっと　みんなの事思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布団を被り　羊数え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝を待って　寝れない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:03.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと明日　楽しくなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:20.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気持ちが強さに変わって　あたしを包む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:30.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔が希望を伝えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日がきっと来る

